PrecisOrder authorizing the National Capital Commission to grant an Easement (ES-865) to the CANADA MORTGAGE AND HOUSING CORPORATION, for a term of 99 years, over and across a strip of land situated near the Queensway-Aviation Parkway intersection in Gloucester, Ontario, for the installation of sewer works connecting its storm-water retention pond to the Cyrville Drain.
